Thanks.

26
00:08:17,530 --> 00:08:20,522
- Ever seen his work?
- Call that work?

27
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:22,691
I call it hot air, not a livelihood.

28
00:08:25,438 --> 00:08:26,632
Never begs from you.

29
