123
00:17:02,254 --> 00:17:04,654
Can you wait a sec? I want to pee.

124
00:17:04,724 --> 00:17:06,052
Keep an eye.

125
00:17:06,726 --> 00:17:07,784
Thanks.

126
00:17:27,747 --> 00:17:30,072
