275
00:42:02,786 --> 00:42:05,584
And my mother left a long time ago...

276
00:42:06,089 --> 00:42:08,284
upped and left, overnight.

277
00:42:08,592 --> 00:42:10,082
Without saying?

278
00:42:10,661 --> 00:42:11,821
